== For reading sources

:: Source
~~ Abstracted description of a source. Includes common actions, and gear for reporting on a source.

:: CodepointIterator
~~ Iteraters for stepping through the codepoints of various sources 

:: TrackingIterator
~~ Tracks, in source-relative coordinates, the position of the iteratore

:: TokenIterator
~~ Transforms the souce contents into a series of simple tokens
